Body: Description: During our health call we discovered multiple host that we no longer have and would like to purge all records/data relating to them from our database.
This is for Auditor Enterprise / transferring back to T1 queue

What We've Learned Updated: Created a list of hosts with the status of offline (Offline Hosts)
Created a custom job (DropFSHost) in the zClone_Sandbox folder that will drop the data for the offline servers from the file system database tables
Scheduled the job --kick this off when there are no File System jobs running
